sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Cliente
    participant G as API Gateway
    participant M as Microservicio (C++)
    participant K as Keycloak
    participant R as Redis

    C->>G: GET /resource (Authorization: Bearer token)
    G->>M: Proxy con token
    
    Note over M: Verificar token localmente
    
    alt Token expirado (por JWT exp)
        M-->>C: 401 Unauthorized
    end
    
    M->>R: GET token:{token_hash}
    
    alt Cache HIT
        R-->>M: userInfo (postgresId, role)
    else Cache MISS
    
        M->>K: POST /realms/{realm}/protocol/openid-connect/token/introspect
        K-->>M: token active + claims (postgresId, role)
        
        M->>R: SETEX token:{hash} (TTL 60s)
    end
    
    Note over M: Validar que postgresId no esté vacío
    
    alt Token válido
        M->>M: Continuar con lógica de negocio
        M-->>C: 200 OK (recurso)
    else Token inválido
        M-->>C: 401 Unauthorized
    end